Uzbekistan: Public service centers, registry offices and notaries will be open for emergencies only as of Mar. 25:
- public service centers assist citizens online and provide service in emergencies only;
- registry offices are open only to register births or deaths;
- notaries assist only with the will, power of attorney, deposit and mortgage-related issues.
